msg_body: College is easy. It's like a riding a bike. Except the bikes on fire. And the grounds on fire. And everything is on fire. And you're in hell.
When you hold the door open and it ends up being 3 students, 6 parents, 10 aliens and the stampede that killed mufasa.
College is like when you go from 1st to 11th place in Mario Kart because you slipped on your own damn banana.

Hello, it's me. I was wondering if I could get a grade above a C. I haven‘t gone over anything. They say the library‘s supposed to help you, but I ain't done much readings.
Hello, can you hear me?

Attractive Person: Hey, what's up?
Me: Who paid you?
Study hack: Laminate your flash cards. Not only will it keep them from smearing, but the teardrops will just roll off
I don't understand the obsession with threesomes... If I wanted to disappoint two people at once I would just go have lunch with my parents
Why is my movie I'm illegally watching online buffering so much? This is not what I didn't pay for.

I'm laying next to my gorgeous sleeping girlfriend and as I sit here wide awake, I can't help but look at her and smile, lovingly counting down the days util I sacrifice her to the almighty dark lord.
Using y=mx+b to calculate the slope of how down hill my life is going.
I don't know how to flirt... so I’ll just make awkward eye contact till we’re married.
Can we please focus on how accurate this is: "Does snapchat seriously think I'm gonna pay $1 to have fake tears coming out my eyes when I can just think about life and get tearsfor free"
When you go to a restaurant that puts the calories on the menu :(
The real walk of shame is when you take all the mugs and plates you've been hoarding in your room down to the kitchen
There is no "i" in "team" but apparently there is one hidden somewhere in "group project.
The biggest turn on ever is when a guy and is hot. Occassionally spicy. Wrapped in tinfoil. And is actually a burrito.

Mozart wrote his first symphony at age 8.
I'm 20 years of age and just rehearsed 5 times what I'm going to say at the drive through
Me when feeling suspiciously relaxed: what responsiblity have I forgotten?

*At the funeral of my crush*
"Still playing hard to get I see..."
I like how the plagiarism section of the syllabus is the same for every class.. Almost like it was copied and pasted there...
